@startuml 06-plan-maintenance-job
actor "Garage Employee" as Employee
participant WebApp
participant "Workshop Mgmt API" as API
database "Event Store\n(SQL Server)" as ES
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "Workshop Mgmt\nEvent Handler" as EH

Employee -> WebApp : Select date & vehicle, plan job
WebApp -> API : PlanMaintenanceJob (HTTP POST)

API -> ES : Load events for WorkshopPlanning aggregate
ES --> API : Event list

note over API : Replay events to\nreconstruct aggregate state

API -> API : Execute command on aggregate
note over API : Produces WorkshopPlanningCreated\nand/or MaintenanceJobPlanned events

API -> ES : Store new events
ES --> API : OK
API -> MQ : Publish MaintenanceJobPlanned
API --> WebApp : 200 OK
WebApp --> Employee : Updated planning page

MQ ->> EH : Deliver MaintenanceJobPlanned
EH -> EH : Update read-model
@enduml
